  "original_title": "\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bc0 \u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9c\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u00a0 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bb0 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna Members of Parliament Urgent Letter to the President",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A group of 16 members of parliament of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna have sent a letter demanding the immediate resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "In this case, in the said letter, they have requested to give an opportunity to an experienced leader who has no corruption charges.",
        "They also pointed out the need to give a chance to a leader who can win a clear parliamentary majority representing the Parliament.",
        "It is noteworthy that the group of parliamentarians of the said Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna includes Dulles Alagaperuma, Channa Jayasumana and Nalaka Kodahewa."
      ],
